<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 563/82 (2), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2090/93 (3), lays down detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1208/81 (4), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1026/91 (5), by establishing the market prices of adult bovine animals on the basis of the Community scale for the classification of carcases; </inglise>
